                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium text-neutral-200 mb-2.5">Colors</h2>
                            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg max-w-[800px]">Our brand utilizes a neutral primary color palette ranging from light to dark grays, ensuring versatility and readability across different designs. The accent palette features vibrant shades of orange, adding warmth and emphasis to key elements while maintaining a professional and cohesive aesthetic.</p>
                            <div class="square-card p-0 mb-4 mt-8">
                                <div class="w-full border-b border-neutral-600 pl-3">Primary</div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-11 gap-4 p-3.5">
                                    <div class="square-card bg-neutral-50 aspect-square"></div>
                                    <div class="square-card bg-neutral-100 aspect-square"></div>
