                            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg max-w-[800px] mb-8">Our brand employs the Satoshi typeface, a versatile and modern sans-serif font designed for optimal readability across digital platforms. It features a neutral aesthetic that complements our color palette, ensuring clarity and professionalism in all typographic applications.</p>
